---
// Animated 2024 → 2030 growth curve drawn on slide entry.
---
<svg viewBox="0 0 800 120" width="100%" style="margin-top:48px;max-width:800px;opacity:0" class="reveal-on-active" data-delay="600">
  <path d="M0 100 Q100 100 150 80 Q200 60 250 60 Q300 60 350 40 Q400 20 500 15 Q600 10 700 5 Q750 3 800 2"
        stroke="var(--lime)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"
        stroke-dasharray="1200" stroke-dashoffset="1200"
        class="growth-line"/>
  <text x="20" y="116" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-size="11" font-family="Space Mono">2024</text>
  <text x="200" y="76" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-size="11" font-family="Space Mono">2026</text>
  <text x="420" y="36" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-size="11" font-family="Space Mono">2028</text>
  <text x="680" y="22" fill="var(--lime)" font-size="12" font-family="Space Mono" font-weight="700">2030</text>
</svg>
